        "title": "Deploy Java War in docker",
        "body": "<p>I want to deploy my war file on my docker<\/p>\n\n<p>DOCKERFILE<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>FROM java:8\nEXPOSE 8080\nADD /name.war name.war\nENTRYPOINT [\"java\",\"-jar\",\"atp.war\"]\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>I build the image<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>docker build -f Dockerfile -t name .\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>But when i try to run it<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>docker run -p 8080:8080 -t name\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>no main manifest attribute, in name.war<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n<p>what is this and how do I solve it?<\/p>\n",
